M107
;TYPE:Custom
; Filament-specific end gcode 
;END gcode for filament

; play sound when print finishes
M300 S1000 P 250
G4 P250
M300 S1000 P 250
G4 P250
M300 S1000 P 75
G4 P425
M300 S1000 P 75
G4 P425
M300 S1000 P 75
G1 Z10.36 F600 ; Move print head up
G1 X5 Y176 F9000 ; present print
G1 Z78.36 F600 ; Move print head further up
G1 Z162 F600 ; Move print head further up
M140 S0 ; turn off heatbed
M104 S0 ; turn off temperature
M107 ; turn off fan
M84 X Y E ; disable motors

; beep three times
M300 S300 P200
G4 P300
M300 S300 P200
G4 P300
M300 S300 P200
